<ITEM>"Deceit is &s;weet to a man." <BIBL>&mdash;<HI>Prov.</HI> xx.</BIBL></ITEM>
</LIST>
<LIST>
<HEAD>COVETOUSNESS.</HEAD>
<ITEM>"Wealth maketh many friends."&mdash;<BIBL><HI>Prov.</HI> xix.</BIBL></ITEM>
<ITEM><PB N="44" REF="024407_0048_0FC70B9B681A1148">"The rich man is wi&s;e."&mdash;<BIBL><HI>Prov.</HI> xxviii.</BIBL></ITEM>
<ITEM>"Money an&s;wereth all things."&mdash;<BIBL><HI>Ecc.</HI> x.</BIBL></ITEM>
</LIST>
<LIST>
