<ITEM>"In much wi&s;dom is much grief."&mdash;<BIBL><HI>Ecc.</HI> i.</BIBL></ITEM>
<ITEM>"Lay hold on folly."&mdash;<BIBL><HI>Ecc.</HI> ii.</BIBL></ITEM>
<ITEM>"Folly is &s;et in great dignity."&mdash;<BIBL><HI>Ecc.</HI> x.</BIBL></ITEM>
</LIST>
<LIST>
