<DIV2 TYPE="list of instruments">
<HEAD>PHILOSOPHICAL APPARATUS.</HEAD>
<P><HI>A curious new invented magic Lanthorn</HI>: very u&s;eful for the&s;e who are at the head of affairs. This Machine was con&s;tructed by an able Arti&s;t, under <HI>Lord North's</HI> immediate direction, for the amu&s;ement of the good people of England. The Spectators are gratified with an <HI>illuminated</HI> view of the fictitious objects pre&s;ented, but kept totally in the dark with re&s;pect to the <HI>real</HI> objects around them.</P>
<P><HI>Multiplying Gla&s;&s;es;</HI> whereby the numbers of an Enemy may be greatly encrea&s;ed to cover the di&s;|grace of a Defeat, or enhance the glory of a Victory.</P>
