<PB N="167" REF="024407_0171_0FC709D38C7AAFD8">
the&s;e are a variety of real and &s;uppo&s;ed Succe&s;&s;es of the Briti&s;h Generals in America.</P>
<P><HI>A complete Electrical Apparatus,</HI> with improve|ments, for the the u&s;e of the King and his Mi|ni&s;ters. This Machine &s;hould be exerci&s;ed with great caution; otherwi&s;e, as experience hath &s;hown, the operator may unexpectedly <HI>receive</HI> the &s;hock he intends to give&mdash;<HI>Pocket gla&s;&s;es</HI> for &s;hort-&s;ighted Politicians.</P>
