<HEAD>XIII. THE CONSTITUTION.</HEAD>
<P>THE hon. chief ju&s;tice <HI>M'Kean;</HI> the hon. judge <HI>Atlee;</HI> the hon. judge <HI>Ru&s;h</HI>&mdash;in their robes of of|fice; &s;eated in a lofty ornamented car, in form of a
